snippet.title: I Spy Challenger! - Gameboy Advance Playthrough - Part 1 (no commentary) HD
snippet.description:
Support the channel for $1 per month on Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/ReplayingClassics
_____________________________________________ 
I Spy Challenger! playthrough without commentary on the Gameboy Advance part 1. If you enjoy my content remember to like and subscribe. Also if you want to see me play any of your favourite games leave a comment below.

I Spy Challenger! is being played on Visual Boy Advance-M 2.1.4 in High Definition Widescreen mode with xBRZ 6x display filter.
_____________________________________________
Visual Boy Advance-M 2.1.4  Settings:
Output Module: OpenGL
Display Filter: xBRZ 6x
Scaled Resize: 6x
Retain Aspect Ratio: Off
_____________________________________________
My PC Specs:
CPU: Ryzen 5 3600
GPU: AMD Radeon RX 5500 XT 8GB
Ram: 16GB
